ration rules while ensuring that all unshaded cells can still form a single, connected path. This adjustment helps maintain logical consistency in the puzzle.\n\n--- \n\nThis step-by-step approach ensures that each decision is made with clear reasoning based on the beginner-friendly rulebook.",
